Text: Sony Product Registration Confirmationyou for registering your Sony product on our web site This is a confirmation that you have registered the following DSCF You now qualify for a credit towards the purchase of select accessories at Sony Direct As some conditions apply visit sonydiofferhtml to review offer details restrictions and a list of eligible models Refer to the accessory guide booklet that came with your product to view your accessory options Or call and our trained staff will assist you in finding an accessory for your product To make a purchase call within days of registration Our trained staff is standing by to assist you with your selection Please be prepared to provide the operator with the following information Name Martin Cuilla Code MC Model DSCF Serial Number The unique code above will allow you to redeem this credit one time only on instock accessories Please print and keep this code in a safe place because like a gift certificate it cannot be replaced if lost After you make your accessory purchase a separate credit to your credit card account will be processed within billing cycles Please register your future Sony purchases at productregistration If you have any questions regarding service and support please visit our Service Support web site at support or contact This email is automatically generated If you reply back to this message there will be no one available to assist you Thank you again for your registration
